      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NFS节点就叫Education_GradeSync，这样一眼能看出这是核心服务。AzCopy那边是Education_ContentCDN，负责内容分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图结构画好了。现在加AzCopy节点，然后画NFS指向AzCopy的箭头——这是表示成绩文件从本地推送到CDN对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
