      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，NFS到AzCopy是数据流出方向。另外AzCopy还需要关联一个学生数据库，叫Education_StudentDB，它作为Files标签放在AzCopy旁边说明传输内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
