      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Files标注。不过我发现StudentDB还需要一个独立的Note节点做补充说明，我把它放在图表下方，也叫Education_StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
